# Number Guessing Game

The computer picks a random number between 1 and 100 and the user has to guess it.
The program tells you if your guess is too high or too low.

## How to run
python main.py

## How to run tests
python -m pytest test_main.py

## What I learned
- How to use the random module
- How to use while loops
- How to give hints to the user based on their guess
- How to count number of attempts